name: Intimidating
description:
This piece is to celebrate the Halloween coming.
 
Intimidating is the most uneasy feeling that I have feel, more than when you meet some ghosts or mythical creatures. But I still believe that when there's a evil, there's a kindness too. Contradiction but still have a connection.

That's why in this work, evil and kindness on the same spot (human). We're human, the most unpredictable creatures.
